---
title: Gingery Chili-Lemon Tofu with Charred Veggies and Scallion Rice
description: Inspired by the Chinese-American classic, this lemon tofu recipe has bright and fiery flavours. Generously sauced tofu chunks team up with lightly charred veggies for a satisfying dinner any night of the week.
